08/24/153501_1e887062976cbd5665015a2882e6598d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F153501_1e887062976cbd5665015a2882e6598d.jpg&h=6daa75ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/153502_faf41a43b0e6b777c432732c9f753b33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F153502_faf41a43b0e6b777c432732c9f753b33.jpg&h=93060daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次去喺上諏訪站搭的士上公園</blockquote><br />\n依個咪黃昏之時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，影得麻麻"},{"pid":"96ae87a48c1a996d20d1b9d9e03c8e2d5f7acc76","tid":371750,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T22:13:51.000Z","msg":"諏訪湖四隻角有諏訪大社嘅四間分店<br />\n（南面）上社本宮 前宮<br />\n（北面）下社春宮 秋宮<br />\n<br />\n如果想睇埋下社就下諏訪駅近啲<br />\n<br />\n下諏訪春宮秋宮之間有條小徑<br />\n喺古代中山道一部分<br />\n當年德川末期和宮嫁入大奧時行過<br />\n有唔少歷史景點<br />\n<br />\n有武田玄信粒矢除石嘅慈雲寺<br />\n仲有間古代商店嘅記念屋仔<br />\n伏見屋邸，入面有個阿伯識英文<br />\n有故聽<br />\n<br />\n而且作條路都有溫泉，而且唔貴<br />\n有時間請去埋下諏訪<br />\n<br />\n如果去埋松本城都順路"},{"pid":"6279029eed1a8c8532e8059d6b9dd17ca6f3c793","tid":371750,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/153501_1e887062976cbd5665015a2882e6598d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F153501_1e887062976cbd5665015a2882e6598d.jpg&h=6daa75ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/153502_faf41a43b0e6b777c432732c9f753b33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F153502_faf41a43b0e6b777c432732c9f753b33.jpg&h=93060daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br 